      <div xml:id="NA68-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">(EV: talaivaṉ) ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻi talaivikku uraippāḷāyc ceṟippaṟivuṟīiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante prevented [him from] going as one speaking to HER while [HE] was behind the fence.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA68">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            viḷaiyā ṭāyamō ṭōrai yāṭā</l>
<l>            tiḷaiyō rivviṭat tiṟceṟin tirutta</l>
<l>            laṟaṉu maṉṟē yākkamun tēymmeṉak</l>
<l>            kuṟunurai cumanta naṟumala runtip</l>
<l>            poṅkivaru putunīr neñcuṇa vāṭukam </l>
<l>            vallitiṉ vaṇaṅkic collunarp peṟiṉē </l>
<l>            celkeṉa viṭunaṇmaṟ kollō vellumiḻn</l>
<l>            turavuru muraṟu maraiyiru ṇaṭunāṭ</l>
<l>            koṭinuṭaṅ kilaṅkiya miṉṉi</l>
<l>            yāṭumaḻai yiṟuttaṉṟavaṟ kōṭuyar kuṉṟē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">“For young people to be confined to the house, to this place,</l>
<l rend="indent">without playing games with [their] playmates,</l>
<l rend="indent">is not at all virtue. We want to play for [our] hearts to enjoy the</l>
<l rend="indent">new waters that rise bubbling in the river with fragrant blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent3">burdened with bits of foam [saying] ‘all gain will dwindle'.”</l>
<l>If [we] obtained someone to bow submissively [and] speak [thus],</l>
<l>wouldn’t she give in, saying “you may go”?</l>
<l rend="indent4">Spitting light,</l>
<l rend="indent3">at midnight in half darkness when strong thunder murmurs,</l>
<l rend="indent3">flashing so that the creepers shine in a flicker,</l>
<l>playing rain has been tarrying on his hill high with peaks.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
